title: New Country Magazine Holiday Special 320cbr1995 Christmas Music
description:
Source: 1995 CD
 
New Country Magazine Holiday Special 320cbr (Big Papi) 1995 Christmas Music


In case you are wondering "New Country" was a term coined for 90's country music. I'm not an expert but New Country really blurred the lines between rock and country music. It was like making rock music but using country twang in the voice. My opinion only...not an expert. And...some of these artists are from the 80's - Big Papi
